lines.text: Darling, we have passed the rocks and here are the safe waters beyond.
I could never live under the shadow of my broken word!

[to Lord Bracondale, after he has saved her life a second time]
Fate seems to send you to me when I most need you, Lord Bracondale.
I wish he weren't quite so impossible.
My dear, no man with millions is impossible.
No, but I'm afraid he's going to.
